title: Djokovic humbles Nadal to extend Beijing dynasty
text: Oct. 12, 2015 | 12:07 AM Djokovic humbles Nadal to extend Beijing dynasty Novak Djokovic of Serbia raises his trophy during the award ceremony after winning the men's singles final match against Rafael Nadal of Spain at the China Open Tennis Tournament in Beijing, China, October 11, 2015. REUTERS/Stringer Share Agence France Presse   A version of this article appeared in the print edition of The Daily Star on October 12, 2015, on page 12. Recommended
